{"tid":2280092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報華為以150億美元出售榮耀業務","createTime":"2020-11-10T08:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T06:54:00.000Z","uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"125d85eeab02ff3c20e955e0d9babc5146744ab1","tid":2280092,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559247-20201110.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559247-20201110.htm&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Inr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=18fab6fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559247-20201110.htm&h=0febc161\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559247-20201110.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n外電指，華為計劃以150億美元，即大約1000億元人民幣，出售旗下較低價格智能手機榮耀的業務，包括品牌、研發能力及供應鏈管理，給神州數碼及深圳市政府牽頭的財團，預計最快星期日宣布。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，神州數碼會以銀行貸款為交易所需進行融資，至少有3間由深圳市政府支持的投資公司加入，每間持股10%-15%，神州數碼將成為第2大股東，交易完成後，榮耀將會保留大部份團隊及7千多名員工， 並在3年內上市。<br />\n<br />\n華為、神州數碼及深圳市政府都未有回應有關報道。"},{"pid":"7664f5922b73b963eb6833723ed65bb4d6f693fb","tid":2280092,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"想金蟬脫殼?"},{"pid":"45d866932a0a273c8acb4a6e89e228a0eec962a2","tid":2280092,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7664f5922b73b963eb6833723ed65bb4d6f693fb","tid":2280092,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"想金蟬脫殼?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:45:38.000Z","msg":"借屍還魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4874feb6f252e20ba97282fe6c0cd963e3c26dea","tid":2280092,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"買垃圾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi